Class UnsafeTableValueHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.keva.table.TableValueHistory
      • gov.ornl.keva.table.UnsafeTableValueHistory

  • public class UnsafeTableValueHistory
extends TableValueHistory
    Store a history of values. These values must all belong to a single branch. This implementation is not thread-safe!
